{"tid":1137390,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"保險公司疑似呃人入行手法？","createTime":"2019-05-03T17:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T18:00:28.000Z","uid":26189,"like":17,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"42b4a1bb3b22c769dce0a7878f37b32146eb5a78","tid":1137390,"uid":26189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"話說最近返part time 話請event helper 80蚊一個鐘 心諗fatfat啦  跟住去到 一睇公司名 屌你保險公司黎 跟住interview 叫我之後上training  係關於cash flow 話呢份工就係去八大睇住啲大學生玩 心諗都唔錯呀 幾hea人工又ok 跟住就黎料training 完又叫我揀一個日子test返個日training 既野 之後test個時就捉住我講左個幾鐘話我打工冇用 一世買唔到樓 好似想洗我腦咁 然後佢再同我講話佢地有個course 係俾人學點賺財務自由 被動收入咁 最後我又傻傻地上左一堂course 心諗又唔洗錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知！佢超級洗腦式吹大自己公司 話我地做保險有幾好幾好 幾個鐘得個15分鐘食晚飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls 都有幾多人上個course 全部大學生 佢地個個都上唔止一堂 走火入魔咁 想問呢比有冇人又係俾人呃左上去啲新人班到 佢地既目的係咩 有冇人知道？我就唔撚信佢哋真係咁有熱誠唔睇成本培訓新人入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee178034c611b818d8db7ed01f08fddbef7910df","tid":1137390,"uid":26189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d545f0034e7fd9440c4aea8d6122c7021298f1f","tid":1137390,"uid":26189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c1872ef1e40ea3c66cb36cd9366bb1acf58da8","tid":1137390,"uid":36478,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809b843f3ed1e832407a48ae5cf090679ed48320","tid":11373